    "description": "<p>Until the spell ends, the target's Speed is doubled, it gains a +2 bonus to AC, it has advantage on Dexterity saving throws, and it gains one additional action on each of its turns. This action can be used to make a single weapon attack, or to take the Dash, Disengage, Hide, or Use an Object action.</p><p>When the spell ends, the target is tired and cannot move or take actions until after its next turn.</p><p><strong><em>Cast at Higher Levels.</em></strong> Target one additional creature for each slot level above 3rd. All targets of this spell must be within 30 feet of each other.</p>",
